This is the code from the Viewport.java ([source](https://github.com/libgdx/libgdx/blob/master/gdx/src/com/badlogic/gdx/utils/viewport/Viewport.java#L64-L66))

``` java
    /** Configures this viewport's screen bounds using the specified screen size and calls {@link #apply(boolean)}. Typically called
